<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 10:07:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“奇迹时代”：以色列极右翼部长对约旦河西岸定居点扩建感到高兴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/era-of-miracles-israeli-far-right-minister-rejoices-at-west-bank-settlement-expansion/00000190-8bf3-dbb7-afbf-cffb409f0000</link><description>国家宣教部长奥里特·斯特罗克 (Orit Strock) 参观了希伯伦附近即将合法化的前哨基地，并表示在那里定居是她的首要任务</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 07:15:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/era-of-miracles-israeli-far-right-minister-rejoices-at-west-bank-settlement-expansion/00000190-8bf3-dbb7-afbf-cffb409f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军于 10 月 7 日下令汉尼拔指令，防止哈马斯俘虏士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/idf-ordered-hannibal-directive-on-october-7-to-prevent-hamas-taking-soldiers-captive/00000190-89a2-d776-a3b1-fdbe45520000</link><description>“人们陷入了疯狂的歇斯底里，在没有经过核实的信息的情况下就开始做出决定”：《国土报》获得的文件和证词显示，汉尼拔的行动命令，指示使用武力防止士兵被俘虏，是在被渗透的三个军队设施中使用的。哈马斯也可能危及平民</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 03:22:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/idf-ordered-hannibal-directive-on-october-7-to-prevent-hamas-taking-soldiers-captive/00000190-89a2-d776-a3b1-fdbe45520000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯人质谈判进入关键阶段，外国领导人对内塔尼亚胡混杂的信息感到困惑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/with-hostage-talks-in-crucial-phase-foreign-leaders-are-perplexed-by-pms-mixed-messages/00000190-89af-dd37-a5f7-bbef61630000</link><description>过去几天，国际社会一直试图弄清楚内塔尼亚胡的意图。他是否希望达成一项能够实现更广泛停火的协议，或者这些举措是为了在协议最终遭到破坏之前安抚公众舆论并缓解国际压力？</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 02:38:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/with-hostage-talks-in-crucial-phase-foreign-leaders-are-perplexed-by-pms-mixed-messages/00000190-89af-dd37-a5f7-bbef61630000</guid></item><item><title>从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了数十枚火箭；以色列男子被弹片重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article-live/cia-chief-to-meet-with-israel-egypt-and-qatar-ahead-of-renewed-hostage-deal-talks/00000190-8ae4-d41a-a3dc-9ef4d5080000</link><description>周日的示威活动要求在“抵抗日”达成人质协议，以对抗政府，距 10 月 7 日已过去 9 个月了。 ■ 一名 28 岁男子在从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射的火箭弹中被弹片严重炸伤。在人质协议第一阶段实现持久停火并接受协议；内塔尼亚胡称“差距仍然存在” ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告称，在加沙流离失所者学校住宿的袭击中至少有 16 人死亡 ■ 以色列军队在黎巴嫩境内深处的无人机袭击中杀死了真主党特工</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 01:59:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article-live/cia-chief-to-meet-with-israel-egypt-and-qatar-ahead-of-renewed-hostage-deal-talks/00000190-8ae4-d41a-a3dc-9ef4d5080000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，以色列的新要求预计将推迟人质交易的完成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-demands-are-expected-to-delay-completion-of-hostage-deal-sources-say/00000190-89b1-d8b2-a3b6-fdff13d80000</link><description>摩萨德负责人大卫·巴尼亚向调解员提供了以色列新的保留清单，其中一些是关于在当地实施停火的措辞。据以色列消息人士称，谈判预计至少持续三周才能达成协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 00:19:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-demands-are-expected-to-delay-completion-of-hostage-deal-sources-say/00000190-89b1-d8b2-a3b6-fdff13d80000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日涉嫌杀害一名巴勒斯坦人的三名以色列人中至少有一人不太可能受到指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/some-of-the-israelis-suspected-of-murdering-palestinian-on-oct-7-unlikely-to-be-charged/00000190-8970-d41a-a3dc-9d70f1e70000</link><description>这三名嫌疑人不属于以色列安全部队，涉嫌射杀当天早上从加沙进入以色列的一名手无寸铁的巴勒斯坦人。调查消息传出后，MK Gantz 表示，所有 10 月 7 日进入以色列的加沙人“都将被判处死刑”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 00:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-07/ty-article/.premium/some-of-the-israelis-suspected-of-murdering-palestinian-on-oct-7-unlikely-to-be-charged/00000190-8970-d41a-a3dc-9d70f1e70000</guid></item><item><title>1967 年西墙标志性照片中的伞兵去世，享年 81 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/paratrooper-in-iconic-1967-western-wall-photograph-dies-at-81/00000190-8950-d0d9-a1f9-aff6187a0000</link><description>伊扎克·伊法特（Yitzhak Yifat）被拍成了以色列历史上最著名的照片之一，几天后他告诉《国土报》，虽然他不信教，但在那些时刻他“感受到了一些东西”</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 19:37:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/paratrooper-in-iconic-1967-western-wall-photograph-dies-at-81/00000190-8950-d0d9-a1f9-aff6187a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在深入黎巴嫩境内的袭击中杀死真主党特工</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-kills-hezbollah-operative-in-drone-strike-deep-inside-lebanese-territory/00000190-8956-dc2c-a9fa-ed5eb93b0000</link><description>据以色列军方称，这名真主党特工是该组织防空系统的关键专家，参与了针对以色列的各种行动的规划和执行</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 18:58:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-kills-hezbollah-operative-in-drone-strike-deep-inside-lebanese-territory/00000190-8956-dc2c-a9fa-ed5eb93b0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人报告称，加沙流离失所者学校遭到袭击，造成至少 16 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/palestinians-report-at-least-16-killed-in-strike-on-gaza-school-housing-displaced-persons/00000190-891f-d41a-a3dc-9d1ff67f0000</link><description>加沙哈马斯控制的卫生部报告称，努塞拉特难民营内一所收容流离失所者的学校遭到袭击，造成 16 人死亡、数十人受伤，以色列军方称该难民营被用作“哈马斯总部和恐怖分子的藏身之处”</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 18:13:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/palestinians-report-at-least-16-killed-in-strike-on-gaza-school-housing-displaced-persons/00000190-891f-d41a-a3dc-9d1ff67f0000</guid></item><item><title>有报道称谈判取得进展，以色列全国各地抗议人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/israelis-protest-across-the-country-for-a-hostage-deal-amid-reports-of-progress-in-talks/00000190-88e5-dbb7-afbf-cdede4950000</link><description>据报道，以色列和哈马斯之间的谈判取得了进展，全国各地爆发了抗议活动，据称前者已放弃要求以色列承诺在协议第一阶段全面停火的要求</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 17:54:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/israelis-protest-across-the-country-for-a-hostage-deal-amid-reports-of-progress-in-talks/00000190-88e5-dbb7-afbf-cdede4950000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 274 天：巴勒斯坦人报告加沙中央学校遇袭至少 15 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-274-palestinians-report-15-killed-in-attack-on-central-gaza-school/00000190-88da-d776-a3b1-fcded1f50000</link><description>哈马斯管理的卫生部：15 人因加沙流离失所的学校住房袭击而丧生 ■ 哈马斯放弃了以色列在签署协议之前首先承诺永久停火的要求 ■ 以色列国防军称其击中了加沙人道主义区的火箭发射器 ■ 以色列国防军在约旦河西岸打伤了六名巴勒斯坦人;以色列国防军：士兵遭到枪击后开枪 ■ 战争进入 274 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 17:22:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-274-palestinians-report-15-killed-in-attack-on-central-gaza-school/00000190-88da-d776-a3b1-fcded1f50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部发现一名男子死亡；警方怀疑谋杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/man-found-dead-in-northern-israel-police-suspect-murder/00000190-88d2-dbb7-afbf-cddb83a00000</link><description>塔姆拉的死亡事件发生在拿撒勒发生两起杀戮事件之后不到一天 ■ 根据国土报统计，今年有 117 名阿拉伯社区成员被杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 16:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/man-found-dead-in-northern-israel-police-suspect-murder/00000190-88d2-dbb7-afbf-cddb83a00000</guid></item><item><title>中央情报局局长将在重新启动人质协议谈判之前与以色列、埃及和卡塔尔同行会面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-live/hamas-tells-hezbollah-it-agreed-to-proposed-cease-fire-in-gaza-netanyahu-says-gaps-remain/00000190-85b4-d0d9-a1f9-a7f624ec0000</link><description>哈马斯在人质协议第一阶段放弃持久停火的要求并接受协议；内塔尼亚胡称“差距仍然存在” ■ 巴勒斯坦人报告称，在加沙流离失所者学校住宿的袭击中至少有 16 人死亡 ■ 以色列军队在黎巴嫩领土深处的无人机袭击中杀死了真主党特工 ■ 各地发生针对政府、要求释放人质协议的抗议活动以色列</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 02:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-live/hamas-tells-hezbollah-it-agreed-to-proposed-cease-fire-in-gaza-netanyahu-says-gaps-remain/00000190-85b4-d0d9-a1f9-a7f624ec0000</guid></item><item><title>镜头没有说谎，以色列军队有一种运送受伤巴勒斯坦人的新方式：在吉普车的引擎盖上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-idf-has-a-new-way-of-transporting-wounded-palestinians-on-the-hoods-of-jeeps/00000190-8562-dd1f-adb9-ad6ff0ad0000</link><description>上周，不止一名，而是三名受伤、半裸的巴勒斯坦人遭到以色列国防军士兵的羞辱，他们强迫他们躺在滚烫的车辆上，并在杰宁周围游街示众。军方正在淡化这些事件</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 01:50:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-idf-has-a-new-way-of-transporting-wounded-palestinians-on-the-hoods-of-jeeps/00000190-8562-dd1f-adb9-ad6ff0ad0000</guid></item><item><title>针对强大的以色列定居者团体的国际制裁可能会带来惊天动地的影响</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/mounting-international-sanctions-against-israeli-settler-group-could-be-earth-shattering/00000190-853d-dc2c-a9fa-e57d20fa0000</link><description>阿马纳组织与以色列所有银行以及居住在该组织家园的数千名定居者都有联系。加拿大实施的制裁延长可能会引发定居点运动的地震</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 00:10:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/mounting-international-sanctions-against-israeli-settler-group-could-be-earth-shattering/00000190-853d-dc2c-a9fa-e57d20fa0000</guid></item><item><title>99 年，奥斯陆协议的制定者为以色列的未来描绘了严峻的愿景。事实证明它非常准确</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-99-ron-pundak-had-a-stark-vision-of-israels-future-it-was-painfully-accurate/00000190-8478-db02-a398-8d7901ad0000</link><description>《奥斯陆协议》的缔造者之一罗恩·庞达克 (Ron Pundak) 在 1999 年对以色列 2025 年的情况做出了噩梦般的预测。今天，在他去世十年后，这一切已经非常接近现实了</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 23:29:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/in-99-ron-pundak-had-a-stark-vision-of-israels-future-it-was-painfully-accurate/00000190-8478-db02-a398-8d7901ad0000</guid></item><item><title>甚至在哈马斯做出回应之前，内塔尼亚胡就试图破坏人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tried-to-derail-the-hostage-deal-even-before-hamas-responded/00000190-7f58-df13-a798-ffd8b3ad0000</link><description>以色列总理渴望在任何协议中发挥作用，他的同谋贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇也有同样的态度。 -法西斯立法</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 21:01:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tried-to-derail-the-hostage-deal-even-before-hamas-responded/00000190-7f58-df13-a798-ffd8b3ad0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在加沙人质协议第一阶段放弃了持久停火的要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/hamas-informs-hezbollah-it-agrees-to-gaza-cease-fire-deal-netanyahu-gaps-remain/00000190-849d-d161-abd0-cdbddaec0000</link><description>真主党周五还表示，一旦加沙地带休战生效，真主党将停止战斗。然而，以色列总理内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，双方之间“仍然存在分歧”</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 20:58:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/hamas-informs-hezbollah-it-agrees-to-gaza-cease-fire-deal-netanyahu-gaps-remain/00000190-849d-d161-abd0-cdbddaec0000</guid></item><item><title>如何在不影响间谍的情况下处理情报警告：阿什拉夫·马尔万的教训</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-to-address-an-intelligence-warning-without-putting-the-spy-at-risk/00000190-83fe-dff5-a5d2-8ffe47540000</link><description>以色列如何能够在不暴露其身份的情况下对情报官员的严重警告做出回应？ 1973 年 10 月的经验教训可能在 50 年后仍然适用</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 19:54:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-to-address-an-intelligence-warning-without-putting-the-spy-at-risk/00000190-83fe-dff5-a5d2-8ffe47540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 273 天：美国官员称哈马斯在停战谈判中做出重大转变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-273-firefighting-teams-subdue-most-fires-in-north-israel/00000190-83ce-de6b-a9d0-c7cf057c0001</link><description>以色列摩萨德负责人启程前往卡塔尔继续停战谈判 ■ 美国高级官员称，哈马斯立场重大调整后，停战谈判取得“突破” ■ 真主党副领导人：扩大与以色列的战斗目前“不可行” ■ 消防队在黎巴嫩猛烈火箭弹袭击后，以色列北部的大部分大火得到扑灭 ■ 战争进入 273 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jul 2024 17:01:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-273-firefighting-teams-subdue-most-fires-in-north-israel/00000190-83ce-de6b-a9d0-c7cf057c0001</guid></item></channel></rss>